text: Cuiabá Esporte Clube, commonly known as Cuiabá, is a Brazilian football team based in Cuiabá, Mato Grosso. They won the Campeonato Mato-Grossense five times and in the Série D once. ==Achievements== * Campeonato Mato-Grossense: ** Winners (5): 2003, 2004, 2011, 2013, 2014 * Copa Governador do Mato Grosso: ** Winners (1): 2010 Category:Brazilian football clubs Category:Mato Grosso
title: Cuiabá Esporte Clube
